May Aligwe, first wife of popular actor Yul Edochie, has reacted to his post unveiling his second wife and son. The 40-year-old movie producer on Wednesday shared photos of an infant and a pregnant woman. Yul Edochie announced the infant with his mother as the latest additions to his family. According to Yul, it was time the world met “Star Dike Munachimso Yul-Edochie” born by his second wife, Judy Austin Muoghalu.   Yul Edochie announces second wife     Yul Edochie unveils son with second wife     Nagging, quarrelling bond couples – Shan George   The film star also noted he loves his infant son as much as his other kids from his first wife. Reacting to her husband post, the first wife took to the comment section to express her grief in form of a prayer. She wrote: “May God judge you both.”